org.digijava.kernel.ampapi.endpoints.settings

Class SettingsDefinitionsEndpoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.digijava.kernel.ampapi.endpoints.settings.SettingsDefinitionsEndpoint

  • public class SettingsDefinitionsEndpoint
extends java.lang.Object
    This endpoint returns settings definitions for each module. Settings definitions were designed to be consumed by Settings Widget.

    See also SettingField.
